body:
Hi,

I'm Josh, a professional software engineer from Australia currently in the US. I live and breathe software development, starting from an early with MBasic 1.0 on an Osborne Executive running CPM/86. I have spent the last 15 or so years building systems in a variety of industries including eCommmerce, healthcare, finance, transportation, and various government agencies.

Currently, I'm looking for my next opportunity to be part of something awesome in Seattle, WA. Hit me up via [My LinkedIn profile](https://www.linkedin.com/in/joshuamckinney) and let's get acquainted.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
